                  </hi> On Saturday night, 31st May, I saw the ticket 143—it was in William Smith's handwriting—the amount was 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I put it into the bag myself—I saw it handed to George Smith, with presented the tally 143.</p>
